<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You've Been Added to a Healthcare Program - HealthHub</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; color: #2c3e50; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color:
      #f8f9fa; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #36d1dc 0%, #5b86e5 100%); padding: 25px;
      text-align: center; color: white; border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px; } .logo { margin-bottom: 10px; } .content {
      padding: 30px; background-color: #ffffff; border-left: 1px solid #e6e9ec;
      border-right: 1px solid #e6e9ec; } .footer { padding: 20px; text-align:
      center; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d; background-color: #f2f4f6;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; border:
      1px solid #e6e9ec; } .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2980b9); color: white;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 30px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight:
      bold; box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); transition: transform
      0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; } .button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); } .highlight { color: #3498db;
      font-weight: bold; } .divider { height: 1px; background-color: #e6e9ec;
      margin: 20px 0; } .program-details { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding:
      15px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #e6e9ec; margin: 15px 0; }
      .hospital-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-right: 10px; color: #ffffff; }
      .info-box { background-color: #e1f5fe; border-left: 4px solid #03a9f4;
      padding: 12px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 3px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
          <span class="hospital-icon">⚕️</span>
        </div>
        <h1>HealthHub</h1>
        <p>Your Health Journey Update</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{patientName}},</p>
        <p>
          We're writing to inform you that
          <span class="highlight">Dr. {{doctorName}}</span>
          has added you to the following healthcare program:
        </p>

        <div class="program-details">
          <h2>{{programName}}</h2>
          <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
          <p>{{programDescription}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p>This program is designed to help you achieve better health outcomes
            and provide structured support for your specific healthcare needs.</p>
        </div>

        <p>Here's what you can expect from this program:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Regular check-ins with your healthcare team</li>
          <li>Personalized care tailored to your health goals</li>
          <li>Coordination between different healthcare providers</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          To view the complete details of your program and access related
          resources, please log in to your patient portal:
        </p>

        <p style="text-align: center">
          <a href="{{patientPortalLink}}" class="button">Access Your Patient
            Portal</a>
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          If you have any questions about this program or need assistance,
          please contact your healthcare team at +254742796954
          or reply to this email.
        </p>

        <p>
          To your health,<br />
          <span class="highlight">The HealthHub Team</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This email was sent to
          {{patientEmail}}
          because you are registered with HealthHub Medical Center.
        </p>
        <p>© {{currentYear}} HealthHub Medical Center. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{notificationPreferencesLink}}">Notification Preferences</a>
          |
          <a href="{{privacyPolicyLink}}">HIPAA Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href="{{termsOfServiceLink}}">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>